			Our <a href="http://216.240.130.13/forums/index.cfm?currentsiteid=22">discussion forums</a> have been streamlined and revamped! I've cut down on the amount of categories into a few smaller areas where different categories can be focused on.  I've also learned that the Gamer's Lounge will be slated for launch with all of it's features in about a month, meaning customizable profile images, colors to match EQrealms, and so on.  So feel free to hit up those forums and yak away or ask questions I'll check them daily. 
