			Well I guess nobody really likes updating EQrealms as much as I do, so here I am again!  I've been gathering up a bunch of information lately on Sebilis, Kaesora, Droga, Dalnir, Karnors, and hopefully Howling Stones soon.  I'm going to be beefing up the different item sections and then adding dungeon guides one by one.  Please continue to send in any quests, item pics, bugs/mistakes with the site, or other things I appreciate the help. 
			<br><br>
			
			
		
	
			<a name="201"></a>
			<FONT COLOR="4a0000"><B>Backdoor Virus Alert</B></FONT><BR>
			<TABLE border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="1"><TR>
			<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2"><a href="responses.cfm?id=201">Add Comment</A> (0)</font> &nbsp; &nbsp;</TD>
			<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2"><a href="index.cfm?category_id=4" title="View news of this category"><font color="ca0000">Dev Quotes</font></a></font> &nbsp; &nbsp; </TD>
			<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2">Server: N/A</font>&nbsp;</TD>
			<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2">Posted By: <A HREF="mailto:dantes@eqrealms.com">Dantes</A></font> &nbsp; &nbsp; </TD>
			<TD bgcolor="#aaaaaa"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="-2">03:22 PM</font>&nbsp;</TD>
			</TR></TABLE>
			Some people will try anything to steal your login/password, here's a quote from Abashi concerning a new scam program everyone should avoid;<BR>

<BLOCKQUOTE><i>
Hello all,<BR><BR>
Another scam has been found. Someone has put up a web page offering a utility called the "EverQuest Connection Enhancer". This is actually a program that installs a backdoor virus (Norton: Backdoor.SubSeven) that will allow people access to your EverQuest login information as well as other private information on your system. We are going to try to get the site closed down.<BR><BR>

As always, we recommend that you do not use any programs from an untrusted source.<BR><BR>

-Gordon
</BLOCKQUOTE></i> 
			<br><br>
			
			
		
	
